                                "The expanded exemption adopted by the Agencies includes qualified mortgages defined by the Bureau in any of its regulations, such as loans described in \u00a7 1026.43(e) as well as \u00a7 1026.43(f). Thus, qualified mortgages exempt from the HPML appraisal rules include loans subject to the Bureau's ability-to-repay rules that:", 
